Path: This week in Nu #37
Content:
nespera improved our filesize unit parser (
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/1693] #1693
), added docs for 
``wrap``
 (
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/1704] #1704
)
fdncred parallelized plugin loading, dramatically speeding it up (
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/1694] #1694
)
JosephTLyons cleaned up some logic in file handling (
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/1692] #1692
), added directory sizes to 
``ls``
 (
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/1696] #1696
), fixed some 
``ls``
 column bugs (
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/1705] #1705
)
jzaefferer added docs for 
``alias``
 (
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/1697] #1697
), fixed the new 
``to``
 and 
``from``
 subcommand docs (
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/1711] #1711
, 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/1712] #1712
, 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/1715] #1715
)
jonathandturner fixed a bug where 
``each``
 wasn't showing errors (
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/1707] #1707
), added subcommands and changed 
``to-*``
 and 
``from-*``
 to use them (
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/1708] #1708
), added 
``with-env``
 command to temporarily add environment variables (
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/1717] #1717
), added bash-like shorthand for 
``with-env``
 (
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/1718] #1718
), fixed a bug when changing to Windows drive (
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/1721] #1721
)
thegedge fixed an issue with externals closing gave a pipeline error (
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/1723] #1723
)
andrasio renamed 
``edit``
 to 
``update``
 (
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/1724] #1724
) and 
``pick``
 to 
``select``
 (
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/1725] #1725
)
1ntEgr8 added a 
``start``
 command to automatically load apps based on file type (
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/1727] #1727
)
JesterOrNot improved our Gitpod integration (
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/1728] #1728
)
